          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-1352 recovery: rework recovery timer functions",
        "message": "LU-1352 recovery: rework recovery timer functions\n\n- there is a race in check_and_start_recovery_timer, which causes\n  the recovery timer is armed more than one time.\n- in reset_recovery_timer, the remaining time could be negative.\n\nthis patch includes several patches landed after b2_1 was released\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/1292\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/1620\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/1722\n\nthe above patches are introduced with IR(Imperative Recovery), and\nthis patch excludes code lines of IR.\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ia4ec804c58c4c94c2a33a3649acdd40d000f45d2\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b2_1"
    }
